bilingual.source: He was hit in the leg by a bullet.
bilingual.target: 他被一颗子弹击中了腿。

bilingual.source: He took a bullet out of his pocket.
bilingual.target: 他从口袋里掏出一颗子弹。

bilingual.source: The speed of a rifle bullet is very fast.
bilingual.target: 步枪子弹的速度非常快。
这颗子弹的弹道非常精准。

bilingual.source: The bullet pierced through the target with ease.
The bullet can penetrate the thickest armor.
bilingual.target: 子弹可以穿透最厚的盔甲。

list.abstract: 概述：Bullet是一个开源的物理模拟计算引擎，世界三大物理模拟引擎之一（另外两种是Havok和PhysX）。广泛应用于游戏开发和电影制作中。Bullet也是AMD开放物理计划成员之一。

来自英国威尔士南部Bridgend大学的四位学生于1999年组建了Bullet for My Valentine。最初，他们曾以“Jeff kill john”和“Opportunity In Chigago”为名，专门翻唱一些Nirvana与Metallica的作品。2002年，乐队曾在一张双CD的威尔士乐队合辑中发表了一首作品。之后，贝司手Nik Crandle退出，新成员Jason James填补了这一位置的空缺。从此，乐队也换掉了以前那些土气的名字，正式更名为Bullet For My Valentine（我的情人节子弹）。

yingyinNormal.en: It's called a bullet. You shoot people with them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这叫子弹，朝人开枪时用的。

yingyinNormal.en: Every rivet that they strike could have been a bullet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们敲击的每颗铆钉都有可能是子弹。

yingyinNormal.en: What else would explains a bullet miraculously curving through the air?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这就能很好的解释，为何子弹在空中能奇迹般的转弯。

yingyinNormal.en: So what? What's it to you if I end up with a bullet in the head? Nothing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那又怎样？要是我在你面前被子弹爆了头，会怎样？不会怎样。

yingyinNormal.en: Your honor, this bullet is clearly a warning of violence to come to Mrs. Ruiz and her family.
yingyinNormal.zh: 法官阁下，这枚子弹无疑是对鲁伊兹夫人及其家人的暴力威胁。

yingyinNormal.en: The bullet grazed his cortical shield. It's not pretty, but he should be functional. Wake up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 子弹擦过了他脑皮层表面，虽然挺严重，但是他应该还是可以运作的。醒来。

yingyinNormal.en: The bullet? The metal was developed by a private company. What company? Lexcorp. Lex Luthor?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那颗子弹呢？金属是由一家私营企业生产的。什么公司？莱克斯集团。莱克斯·卢瑟？

yingyinNormal.en: The bullet to the thorax was the one that killed him. The other two shots, the one to the right shoulder and the stomach, they were survivable.
yingyinNormal.zh: 胸部的子弹是致命伤，其他两处枪击，即右肩和胃部的，都不是致命的。

yingyinNormal.en: What a surprise. Now what? Just this morning, Mrs. Ruiz received this bullet in her mailbox, with the letters "L.C." written on the side.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真是个惊喜啊，又耍什么招？今晨鲁伊兹太太在邮箱发现了这枚子弹，上面写着「L.C.」。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, I like all kinds of trains, steam, diesel, coal, elevated, bullet. I defy you to name a train that I don't like.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我喜欢所有火车啊，蒸汽火车，柴油火车，煤炭火车,高架列车,子弹列车。你有本事就说出个我不喜欢的火车。

yingyinNormal.en: You don't have to use a silver bullet. But if you forge one, well, then we don't have to depend upon the kindness of monsters.
yingyinNormal.zh: 并不是非得使用银子弹，但如果造一颗出来，那么，我们就不必再仰仗怪物们的怜悯了。

yingyinNormal.en: As a deterrent. A silver bullet to keep in reserve, to use against the Kryptonians, so the day does not come, madam, when your children are waving daisies at a reviewing stand.
yingyinNormal.zh: 作为一种威慑手段，一颗随时准备好的银子弹，可以用来对付氪星人，这样那一天就不会到来，女士，你的孩子站在阅兵台上挥舞雏菊的那一天。

yingyinNormal.en: Merciful thing would be to put a bullet in me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 仁慈点，一枪打死我好了。

yingyinNormal.en: He'd use it like an outline, with a header followed by bullet after bullet, and sometimes even sub-bullets.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他会写上大纲，跟在主题后一个再接着一个个要点，甚至还有副标题！

yingyinNormal.en: One out of four presidents gets shot at. One out of every ten dies from a bullet wound.
yingyinNormal.zh: 四个总统里就有一个遭过枪击，十个总统里有一个死于枪伤。

yingyinNormal.en: I told him to bring up the agenda, suggest bullet points for the SED, but make no demands.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我让他提出议事日程，指出战略对话的关键点，但别提出要求。

yingyinNormal.en: So how did you convince him that he wasn't? I didn't. He put a bullet through his brain. Good luck.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那你是如何成功证明他并不孤独呢？没成功，他朝自己脑袋上开了一枪，祝你好运。

yingyinNormal.en: Our renewable-energy needs are going to come from a variety of resources, it's not going to be one magic bullet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们对可再生能源的需求来源于很多能源不仅仅来源于一种。

yingyinNormal.en: Started in only 2007 at six thousand miles and growing, it's already the longest bullet train network in the world.
yingyinNormal.zh: 2007年才投入使用。现有九千五百多公里列车轨道，仍在增长，而这已是世界上最长的高速列车网络。

yingyinNormal.en: The bullet train's immense speed is achieved with new electrified track across China and aerodynamic trains made from light weight composite materials.
yingyinNormal.zh: 高速列车的风驰电掣得益于遍及全国的新电气化轨道以及轻质复合材料制成的空气动力火车。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: A new job, bigger house or better car will be the magic silver <highlight>bullet</highlight> that will allow us to finally be content.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一份新的工作，更大的房子或更好的汽车将是让我们最终得以满足的灵丹妙药。
